USC MIRC Microservices Plugin

--- Dependencies ---

* Python Video Converter: https://github.com/senko/python-video-converter
  * ffmpeg
* requests

--- Installation ---

Put the plugin in a location discoverable by Microservices, and opy the
usc_mirc_microservices_plugin.cfg.default to usc_mirc_microservices_plugin.cfg,
and adjust the values in the "MIRC" section as required (likely "url",
"username" and "password").
